subject: United States Women's Open (Golf)
Golf
lead_paragraph: Although Paula Creamer has not won an event since, she has five top-five finishes in 10 starts this year and is coming off back-to-back third-place finishes.
snippet: Although Paula Creamer has not won an event since, she has five top-five finishes in 10 starts this year and is coming off back-to-back third-place finishes.
